commits.message:
Better Pinboard script and links on homepage

- Rewrite Pinboard script to fetch all posts and save shared ones
  The old method, fetching just recent posts, gave little
  control over the number of shared posts fetched.
- Make partial for links and add them to homepage
- Lazy load jquery.expander

Lazy-load all optionals

- moment.js
- highlight.js
- octicons

Better icons and spacing

- Use Octicons for Event icons
- More space in lists
- Move text away from icons in project list
- Use moment.js throughout site
- Lazy-load moment.js if needed
